Pane Longbottome.

539
00:59:53,807 --> 00:59:56,687
- Pane Longbottome!
- Dolù, dolù!

540
00:59:56,887 --> 00:59:58,127
Neville, pozor!

541
00:59:59,128 --> 01:00:01,128
Pomoc!

542
01:00:01,847 --> 01:00:04,527
Okamžitě se vrate dolù!

543
